structure.unit: County Treasurers, State Supervision Of County Accounts And County Finances

law.catch_line: Suffolk And Nantucket Counties; Applicability Of Laws
law.text: Sections ten, fourteen, twenty-five to twenty-nine, inclusive, and forty-four shall not apply to Suffolk county, nor shall sections fifteen, sixteen, twenty-five to thirty, inclusive, and thirty-two to thirty-four, inclusive, affect the special laws relative to Suffolk or Nantucket county.
